data.description: Welcome to 4733 Lochmoor, a stunning house located in the desirable Brookland School district. This beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom property is now available, offering a spacious and comfortable living space of 2,102 square feet. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of a wood-burning fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings with loved ones. The sunroom provides an abundance of natural light and a tranquil space to relax and unwind. The walk-in pantry offers ample storage for all your culinary needs, making meal preparation a breeze. This house is situated in a vibrant community that boasts fantastic amenities. Residents can enjoy the refreshing community pool during the summer months or challenge friends to a game of tennis or pickleball on the courts. For families with children, there is also a playground where little ones can have fun and make new friends. Additionally, the clubhouse restaurant is perfect for socializing and enjoying delicious meals without having to leave the comfort of your neighborhood. The separate golf cart garage door is an added convenience for those who enjoy leisurely rides around the neighborhood or hitting the links.
